The paper proposes a method for tensor decomposition, which is a common problem in machine learning and data analysis. The paper also mentions applications in building safety monitoring, patient health monitoring, cyber security, terrorist detection, and fake user detection in social networks, which are all related to different sub-fields of computer science. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
